## 7. Test Strategy

### Test Fixtures

Three fake services under `tests/fixtures/sample_monorepo/` with **intentional conflicts**:

| Service | Key Deps | Purpose |
|---------|----------|---------|
| **ml-service** | requests==2.28.0, pandas==1.5.3 (→numpy<1.23) | Conflict source A |
| **analytics-api** | requests==2.25.1, pandas==2.0.0 (→numpy>=1.23) | Conflict source B |
| **auth-service** | requests==2.28.0, pyjwt==2.6.0 | Clean service (aligns with ml-service) |

This creates:
- **requests conflict**: 2.28.0 vs 2.25.1 (critical — different exact pins)
- **pandas conflict**: 1.5.3 vs 2.0.0 (critical)
- **numpy conflict** (transitive): 1.22.4 vs 1.24.3 (critical — from lockfiles)
- **fastapi conflict**: 0.95.2 vs 0.100.1 (critical — different caret ranges resolve differently)
- **idna conflict** (transitive): 2.10 vs 3.4 (critical)

